| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-4876 — Recovery Inhibition (lockbit3)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: dea147bd-a4d6-5dda-9f06-941b6e2ad220"
